import React from 'react'; import '../Css/ElectronicsFilter.css'; import all from '../Images/5110770.png'; import rice from '../Images/rice.png'; import snacks from '../Images/snacks.png'; import HouseHolds from '../Images/HouseHolds.png'; import Zepto from '../../HomeComponent/Images/Zepto.png'; import SwiggyInstamart from '../../HomeComponent/Images/swiggy-logo.png'; import Blinkit from '../../HomeComponent/Images/Blinkit-yellow-rounded.png'; import JioMart from '../../HomeComponent/Images/JioMart.png'; const GroceryFilter = ({ selectedSubCategory, selectedPrice, onSubCategoryChange, onPriceChange }) => (
onSubCategoryChange('')}>
All Groceries
onSubCategoryChange('food')}>
Rice,Atta,Dal
onSubCategoryChange('snacks')}>
Snack's
onSubCategoryChange('HouseHolds')}>
HouseHold's
onSubCategoryChange('per')}>
Zepto
onSubCategoryChange('SwiggyInstamart')}>
Swiggy Instamart
onSubCategoryChange('Blinkit')}>
Blinkit
onSubCategoryChange('JioMart')}>
JioMart
onPriceChange(parseInt(e.target.value, 10))} />
{selectedPrice} /-
); export default GroceryFilter;
